      "text": "set %items% = [\u0022a\u0022, \u0022b\u0022, \u0022c\u0022, \u0022d\u0022]",
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Audit is the run-wide accumulator of every observed error (per debug.md: \u0022Run-wide accumulator of every error. Survives Pop.\u0022). It records the error at each Call frame it propagates through, not once per unique error \u2014 so 4 inner throws (each handled) \u002B 1 fourth throw \u002B 2 propagation frames for the fourth (goal.call ThrowItem and the foreach goal.call) = 7. The outer handler catches the fourth, so %finalCaught% becomes true.",
